msgid "Apply Recommended Settings"
msgstr "推奨設定を適用"

#: Editor/StudioHomeWindow/StudioHomeWindow.cs:8
msgid "Enter Play Mode Options is disabled"
msgstr "Enter Play Mode Options が無効"

#: Editor/StudioHomeWindow/StudioHomeWindow.cs:9
msgid "Both Domain and Scene reload are enabled"
msgstr "Domain と Scene の両方がリロードされる設定"

#: Editor/StudioHomeWindow/StudioHomeWindow.cs:10
msgid "Domain reload is enabled"
msgstr "Domain がリロードされる設定"

#: Editor/StudioHomeWindow/StudioHomeWindow.cs:11
